  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken and cook until browned on all sides, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, berbere spice, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the dark beer, tomato paste, and chicken broth, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the lid and continue to simmer for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "Serve hot over rice or with injera bread."
